ZH: 不许迟到，否则会罚款。
EN: You must not be late, or else you will be fined.

ZH: 不许随地扔垃圾，保持环境干净。
EN: It's not allowed to litter, keep the environment clean.

ZH: 不许大声喧哗，影响他人休息。
EN: You are not allowed to make loud noises, it disturbs others' rest.

ZH: 不许开车时使用手机，以确保交通安全。
EN: Using a cellphone while driving is not allowed to ensure traffic safety.

ZH: 不许透露任何公司机密信息，以保护商业利益。
EN: You must not disclose any company confidential information, to protect business interests.

ZH: 不许将别人的东西随便拿走，要尊重他人财物。
EN: You are not allowed to take other people's things without permission, respect others' belongings.

ZH: 不许抄袭！这是严重的违规行为。
EN: Plagiarism is not allowed! It is a serious violation.

ZH: 不许冒险！请遵守安全规定。
EN: Taking risks is not allowed! Please follow safety regulations.

ZH: 不许践踏花草，保护自然环境。
EN: Stepping on flowers and plants is not allowed, protect the natural environment.

ZH: 不许玩火，以免发生危险。
EN: Playing with fire is not allowed, in order to avoid danger.

ZH: 不许吸烟，这是禁止的地方。
EN: Smoking is not allowed, it is prohibited in this area.

ZH: 不许违反交通规则，遵守交通法规。
EN: Violating traffic rules is not allowed, obey traffic regulations.

ZH: 不许乱扔垃圾，必须分类投放。
EN: Throwing garbage randomly is not allowed, it must be sorted and disposed of properly.

ZH: 不许随意调整他人的桌椅，保持整齐有序。
EN: Adjusting other people's tables and chairs at will is not allowed, keep it tidy and orderly.

ZH: 不许翘课，要按时上课。
EN: Skipping classes is not allowed, attend classes on time.

ZH: 不许私自进入，必须经过授权。
EN: Entering without permission is not allowed, authorization is required.

ZH: 不许违反考场规定，以免被取消考试资格。
EN: Violating examination room regulations is not allowed, in order not to have your qualification for the exam canceled.

ZH: 不许无故缺席，要给老师请假。
EN: Absences without reasonable cause are not allowed, inform the teacher if you need to take leave.

ZH: 不许对他人进行人身攻击，保持言谈文明。
EN: Making personal attacks on others is not allowed, maintain civilized speech.

ZH: 不许盗窃，违者将受到法律制裁。
EN: Theft is not allowed, violators will be punished by law.
